{
  "url": "https://www.hymnal.net/en/hymn/ns/1085",
  "title": "Give me a drink!",
  "verses": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Every day I would walk to this same, same old well"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hoping all of my thirst it’d quell."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet each time I would still find"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Myself sore, wanting but more—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This water did not satisfy."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then I heard of a spring that would never run dry"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "(For contentment my heart did cry!):"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Whoso drinks shall by no means"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ever thirst; in him will burst"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A fountain of life divine!”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Give me a drink!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For this water I would sing!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I am filled, my thirst’s stilled."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My heart sings again:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Give me a drink!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There’s a fount of life in me!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All I know, it just flows,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Flowing deep within."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I discovered that spring was the Lord Jesus Christ—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He died for me and He’s alive!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of my sins I was forgiv’n,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But much more He had in store—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His very own life to give!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Where then does He give life? Well the Bible tells:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In my spirit where Jesus dwells!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Raised from death, He became breath,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Water too, even true food—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s processed to live in me!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ lives in me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As the Spirit reaching me!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This my song, all day long:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life is flowing free!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s flooding me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As a river ceaselessly!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This my God, to me brought:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The processed Trinity!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If you haven’t yet found what your heart’s looking for,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Come and listen to His own word:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Whoso drinks shall by no means"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ever thirst; in him will burst"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A fountain of life divine!”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Come, oh come see this man! Is He not the Christ?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He came that you would have His life!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just believe, then you will see"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s so real, living, and free—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A genuine prayer’s the way:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ lives in me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As the Spirit flowing free!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yes, in me! I believe!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Take a drink and see!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ lives in you!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s the living water true!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re filled with Him to the brim"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For eternity!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "(repeat chorus)"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    }
